HELP BITWISE                                       Chris Slymon Sep 1984
                                         Updated: Adrian Howard Mar 1992

POP-11 has several operators that perform logical bit manipulations on
integers treated as a sequence of "bits". For full information on these
operators see REF *NUMBERS/Bitwise.

